name: AD LOGO HAT
description:
Alternate Decision Logo Hat. 

83% acrylic/15% wool/2% spandex high profile six panel Flex Fit cap.

SMALL/MED is 6 7/8 to 7 1/4

If your hat absolutly does not fit. I will return your money back. 

*NOTE* I didn't make many, so if the one you want is sold out send me an email at sales@alternatedecision.com and I will make more.

name: Apocalyptic Sonata
description:
Apocalyptic Sonata is a collaboration with the one and only
GODMACHINE!!

After a war torn disaster, the city of Denver is completly engulfed in flames. Every last citizen has either found themselves fleeing the city limits or paying a visit with the reaper. Only the doctor remains to this crumbled city. He plays one last song of despair, one last song for those that perished, one last song for what is no more. This is his Apocalyptic Sonata. 

Apocalyptic Sonata is printed on Anvil's 4.8 oz. 50% Combed ring spun organic cotton in conversion/50% Post-consumer P.E.T. recycled polyester.

** Notice the Cash Register Building in the skyline**

name: Ears to the Streets
description:
Alternate Decision Clothing Signature Series Presents:
"Ears to the Streets" By: Delton Demarest

Ears to the streets is printed on Anvil's Sustainable 4.8 oz. 50% Combed ring spun organic cotton in conversion/50% Post-consumer P.E.T. recycled polyester and is also printed on Bella's 4.2 oz., 100% combed ring spun cotton baby jersey knit t-shirt for the ladies.

Can you believe that Anvil produces this shirt by using RECYCLED PLASTIC BOTTLES!!!??? They are one of the few companies today that utilizes this technology!
